modName: Archery Shop With All Arrows In The Game Archery Shop v1 (Vampire Edition)
descriptionHtml:
Archery Shop v1 (Vampire Edition)
------------------------------------------------------------------
This archery shop is for those who want to play as a vampire on the vampire side and wants to have access to the Bows and weapons on the Dawnguard side… If you are using my other Archery shot then disable that on or your game will crash…. Look at the screenshots for a full list of stuff you will get… This mod took me a long time to make so enjoy…


Features:
All Dawnguard weapons:
All bolts and arrows:
All vampire armor:
2 vampire sets with dark brotherhood stats:
Lots of human blood:
Vampire dog’s respawn also levels to 100:
Free Vampire starter storage:


Note: The key to the storage is in Lord H's room....


-----------------------------------------------------------------
Archery Shop With All Arrows In The Game

http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26900/?
